Skill: frage       Timer: Support      GL: 11    Cost: 50

A fighter builds up intense amounts of rage throughout their life. A
skilled fighter can apply the knowledge gained about rage and it's
pros and cons to weapons, imbuing them with some of their own rage.

Some weapons are simply unable to be imbued with rage, have
magic that would be ruined if you attempted to imbue it with rage, 
or are simply too special to be imbued with rage.

Syntax is: frage <weapon>
